<subSubSection pageId="97" pageNumber="493" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="97.[111,1318,290,645]" pageId="97" pageNumber="493">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[112,247,408,441]" pageId="97" pageNumber="493">Breeding.</emphasis>
Pregnant Sa Pa White-toothed Shrews were recorded from May to mid-July, and mean litter size was three young (range 2-4).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
